             was indicted for <rs id="t18070114-60-off376" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18070114-60-off376" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18070114-60-off376" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18070114-60-cd377" type="crimeDate">24th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18070114-60-off376 t18070114-60-cd377"></join>, one lead cistern, value 3 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18070114-60-victim758" type="victimName">
                     Richard 
                     Scurrah
                  <interp inst="t18070114-60-victim758" type="surname" value="Scurrah"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18070114-60-victim758" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
