                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18070114-60-defend756 t18070114-60-punish380"></join>
               Whipped in Goal
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
